@startuml
title LifeDuo - Comunicação Geral do Sistema (Parte 1)

skinparam backgroundColor #FAFAFA
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 1.5
skinparam sequenceParticipantBorderColor #C2185B
skinparam sequenceParticipantBackgroundColor #F8BBD0
skinparam sequenceActorBorderColor #C2185B
skinparam sequenceActorBackgroundColor #F48FB1
skinparam sequenceLifeLineBorderColor #AD1457
skinparam sequenceArrowColor #880E4F
skinparam sequenceMessageFontColor #880E4F
skinparam noteBorderColor #AD1457
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #FCE4EC
skinparam noteFontColor #880E4F
skinparam databaseBorderColor #C2185B
skinparam databaseBackgroundColor #F8BBD0

actor "Parceiro A" as A
actor "Parceiro B" as B
participant "App Mobile" as Mobile
participant "API Gateway" as API
database "PostgreSQL" as DB
participant "Socket.IO" as WS
participant "NotificationService" as Notif

== Fluxo Principal: Check-in e Conexão Diária ==

A -> Mobile : 1. abrirApp()
Mobile -> API : 2. GET /dashboard
API -> DB : 3. carregarMascote(), missao(), notificacoes()
DB --> API : 4. dadosCarregados
API --> Mobile : 5. dashboard + mascote + missao + notificacoes

A -> Mobile : 6. registrarCheckin(humor)
Mobile -> API : 7. POST /checkins
API -> DB : 8. salvarCheckin()
DB --> API : 9. checkinSalvo
API -> DB : 10. atualizarStreak()
DB --> API : 11. streakAtualizado
API -> Notif : 12. publishEvent(CheckinRecorded)
Notif -> WS : 13. emitRealtime()
WS -> B : 14. notificarParceiro(humor)
API --> Mobile : 15. 201 + streak + xpGanho

== Fluxo Secundário: Mascote e Gamificação ==

A -> Mobile : 16. personalizarMascote(skinId)
Mobile -> API : 17. POST /pet/customize
API -> DB : 18. salvarSkin()
DB --> API : 19. skinSalva
API --> Mobile : 20. mascoteAtualizado()

A -> Mobile : 21. verConquistas()
Mobile -> API : 22. GET /achievements
API -> DB : 23. carregarConquistas()
DB --> API : 24. listaConquistas
API --> Mobile : 25. conquistas + xpTotal

@enduml